        - Auto Water (equips and uses watering can)
        - Auto Collect (rainbow/gold seeds from ground)
        - Auto Buy Seeds (when running low)
        - Anti-AFK (prevents disconnection)
        - Mutation Tracker (displays active mutations)
        - Weather Event Detection
        - Rayfield GUI (full control)
    
    Compatibility:
        - Executors: Solara, Wave, Arceus X, Delta, CodeX, etc.
        - No key system, completely open source.
    
    Usage:
        1. Copy the entire script.
        2. Paste into your executor.
        3. Execute while inside Grow A Garden 2.
        4. Toggle features on/off via the GUI (default key: K).
    
    WARNING: Use at your own risk. This is for educational purposes only.
]]

